Class Sentence

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.semanticweb.cogExp.OWLAPIVerbaliser.TextElement

  • public class Sentence
extends TextElementSequence
    Author:
    fpaffrath This class should be used to handle sentences when verbalizing an explanation. Depending on the set language, German or English is generated.
